This paper discusses the design and implementation of a computing environment for capturing the entire research process, including data and computational details, to enable reproducibility. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL), computer engineering (cs.CE), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), and software engineering (cs.SE).
